%h1 Create short URL

%p Welcome to the Voom.

=form_for @redirect do |f|
  %p
    You want to create a redirection
    %strong from
    http://www.roh.org
    = f.text_field :source
    %strong to
    = f.text_field :target
    (for the target, type full address including ‘http://’)
  %p
    %strong Your name
    = f.text_field :name
  %p
    If applicable,
    %strong name of person who requested short URL
    = f.text_field :stakeholder

  = f.submit "Send creation request"

%p
  See
  =link_to "Current list", redirects_path
  of short URLs.
